"<div>\n<i class=\"NoteType\">\nGeneral\n</i>\n<div class=\"grampsstylednote\">\n<p>\nhttp://www.glendinning.name/ancestry/lmbrtfam/pafg05.htm<br />\nWilliam married Catherine IRVINE daughter of Andrew Hill IRVINE and Mary MCINTYRE on 20 Oct 1891 in Innellan, Dunoon, Argyll. Catherine was born on 3 Dec 1869 in Innellan, Dunoon, Argyll. She died after 31 Mar 1901. Catherine was counted in a census in 1881/1901 in Dunoon, Argyll.<br />\nThey had the following children:<br />\n184 F i Mary McIntyre LAMBERT was born in 1891. She died 1 in 1893 in Dunoon, Argyll.<br />\n185 F ii Christina S LAMBERT was born in 1894 in Dunoon, Argyll. Christina was counted in a census in 1901 in Dunoon, Argyll.<br />\n186 F iii Catherine LAMBERT was born in 1896 in Dunoon, Argyll. Catherine was counted in a census in 1901 in Dunoon, Argyll.<br />\n187 F iv Margaret I LAMBERT was born in 1898 in Kirn, Dunoon, Argyll. Margaret was counted in a census in 1901 in Dunoon, Argyll.<br />\n188 M v John LAMBERT was born in Mar 1901 in Kirn, Dunoon, Argyll. John was counted in a census in 1901 in Dunoon, Argyll.\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
