"<div>\n<i class=\"NoteType\">\nGeneral\n</i>\n<div class=\"grampsstylednote\">\n<p>\nThe 2nd Battalion  traveled thus:<br />\n1904 England: Colchester<br />\n1911 Malta<br />\n1914 Egypt<br />\n1914.11 France and Flanders 8 Div<br />\n1919 Lahore<br />\n1923 Karachi<br />\n1926 Sudan<br />\n1927 England: Colchester<br />\n1931 England: Aldershot 2 Bde<br />\nSo it is likely that George joined the regiment when it was in Colchester (1904-1911)\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
